<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ861218-0207 </DOCNO><HL> Kurzweil Music Systems</HL><DD> 12/18/86</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> KURM </IN><DATELINE> WALTHAM, Mass.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Kurzweil Music Systems Inc. said shareholders approved an increase of 1,111,116 shares in authorized common stock, increasing the total to 8,444,449 shares.    Of the total, 552,596 shares will be reserved for warrants and options and 558,520 shares will be reserved for general corporate purposes.    Kurzweil, which makes digital musical instruments, has 5,853,595 shares outstanding. </TEXT></DOC>